talkOther.text: This place looks very well taken care of!
Gee, there are more books here than in the library!
Wait a minute, this is were they used to keep Blozard! Where is he?!
I can feel we are getting closer to Granner. Better be careful now...
I wonder who is buried here. There is no inscription.
The inscription says: "They who seeks to see the master must demonstrate intelligence"
The inscription says: "The key to the riddle you must uncover"
The inscription says: "Resting by our fourth brother"
